NAME

    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::Legal - common tests to check for copyright
    and license notices

VERSION

      This document describes v0.03 of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::Legal
      Released February 28, 2018 as part of Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Test-Legal.

SYNOPSIS

    in dist.ini

      [Test::Legal]

DESCRIPTION

    This module will add a Test::Legal test as a release test to your
    module

REQUIRES

      * Moose

      * namespace::autoclean

SUPPORT

 Perldoc

    You can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

      perldoc Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::Legal

